if you want to update the lib, the following content can be FYI.

1,get the *.tar.gz file from http://code.google.com/p/google-glog/downloads/list
2,put the *.tar.gz file to your DIR
3,tar -zxvf *.tar.gz file
4,install according to README
	./configure --prefix=$YOUR_INSTALL_PATH
	make
	make install
